Table 3. 1H NMR chemical shifts and relative intensities obtained from simulation of experimental spectrum of Ga(OH)(btec)⋅0.5H2O (MIL-61)

| δ (ppm) | Experimental intensity[^a] (%) | Theoretical intensity[^b] (%) | Attribution |
|---------|---------------------------------|-------------------------------|--------------|
| 4.3     | 18                              | 17                            | OH           |
| 5.5     | 15                              | 17                            | H2O          |
| 8.6     | 41                              | 33                            | aromatics   |
| 10.8    | 13                              | 33                            | COOH         |
| 13.0    | 13                              |                               |              |

[^a]: Values from spectrum decomposition within estimated error of ±4%.
[^b]: Expected values according to chemical formula.
